This uses the Vault and Postgresql provider to declaratively manage roles and databases in a single Postgres instance. The Vault and Postgres provider must be configured appropriately: provider "vault" { address = var.vault_address token = var.vault_token ca_cert_file = var.vault_ca_cert_file
} provider "postgresql" { host = var.postgres_host port = var.postgres_port database = var.postgres_database username = var.postgres_username password = var.postgres_password sslmode = "disable"
}

